{
  "stem": "5758.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I must survive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I really, really walked and walked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This was the famous death march that we experienced.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] feeling of all of us was just-- I'm positive that we lost thousands on that death march.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We arrived in Katowice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They put us on the train, again, in wagons.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Closed the door, and we went [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a day and a night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Actually we did get some hot water, black water or something there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Still no food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We collapsed in the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were not 100 in each wagon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We were less.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Somehow we were able to lie down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were there one whole day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Arrived in a camp, which was called Dora, Nordhausen, at the station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Was Nordhausen was the name of the station.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We were put in barracks there, and we were told that we were going to work underneath the mountains.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "There's a factory in the mountains.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "It was the Harzgebirge, the Harz Mountain, which was near Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we were, again, guarded by SS officers.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Now, when we went to work the next day, into the mountain, into the tunnels of the mountains, we noticed machineries being fabricated, big machines.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Over there they produced the V-1 and the V-2.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "This was produced in Dora, in that factory underneath the mountain, the V1 that you all know so well.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We had to carry heavy metal things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "We had to dig-- dig in the roads, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were to work, again, very hard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "We had couples who guided us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But a lot of prisoners were working on the machineries.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "When we pushed these V-1 machines from one place to another, one of the engineers, a Jewish prisoner, told us, pick up some sand and put it in there.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
